---
titleFull: "ISC2 Tampa Bay – Connecting Tampa Bay's Information Security Professionals"
description: "ISC2 Tampa Bay Chapter connects information security professionals in the Tampa Bay area through networking, education, and community events."
layout: base.njk
---

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>ISC2 Tampa Bay</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Connecting Tampa Bay's Infosec Professionals</p>
    <a href="/membership/" class="btn">Become a Member</a>
  </section>

  <!-- Welcome -->
  <section class="welcome" id="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Tampa Bay's Home for <span>InfoSec</span> Professionals</h2>
      <p>The ISC2 Tampa Bay Chapter brings together information security professionals across the West-Central Florida area. Whether you hold a CISSP, SSCP, or are just getting started in cybersecurity, our chapter offers quarterly meetings, hands-on training, and a community that helps you grow. We're also the official host of the annual BSides Tampa conference.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Photo Gallery -->
  <div class="photo-gallery">
    <img src="/images/meeting2.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter meeting">
    <img src="/images/meeting1.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter event">
    <img src="/images/meeting3.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter networking">
  </div>

  <!-- Features -->
  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Network</h3>
      <p>Our meetings and events allow for networking with Info-Sec professionals across Tampa Bay.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Connect to the community</h3>
      <p>Looking for a way to give back? We offer events that fund raise or educate about security in the local community.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 6h-2v9H6v2c0 .55.45 1 1 1h11l4 4V7c0-.55-.45-1-1-1zm-4 6V3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H3c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v14l4-4h10c.55 0 1-.45 1-1z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Expand your skills</h3>
      <p>We offer member-led classes and boot camps with topics ranging from cloud security to pen-testing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Upcoming Events -->
  <section class="upcoming-preview">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
      {% set eventCount = 0 %}
      {% for event in events %}
        {% if event.date | isFuture and eventCount < 2 %}
          {% set eventCount = eventCount + 1 %}
          <div class="upcoming-card">
            <div class="upcoming-date">
              <span class="upcoming-month">{{ event.date | dateMonth }}</span>
              <span class="upcoming-day">{{ event.date | dateDay }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="upcoming-info">
              <h3>{{ event.title }}</h3>
              <p>{{ event | formatEventTime }} · {{ event.location }}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      <a href="/events/" class="upcoming-link">View All Events →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to connect with Tampa Bay's security community?</h2>
      <div class="cta-banner-actions">
        <a href="/membership/" class="btn">Become a Member</a>
        <a href="/events/" class="btn-outline btn-outline--light">View Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="mission">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Mission <span>Driven</span></h2>
      <p>The Tampa Bay Chapter of ISC2 advances the knowledge of information security professionals, students, and practitioners through education, training, and community engagement.</p>
      <div class="focus-areas">
        <span class="focus-pill">Network Security</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Cloud Security</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Penetration Testing</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Digital Forensics</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Cryptography</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Data Privacy</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Software Security</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">CTF Competitions</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Malware Analysis</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Social Engineering</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">CISSP Training</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">SSCP Training</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mission-highlight">We're also the official host of the annual <strong>BSides Tampa</strong> Information Technology Security Conference.</p>
      <p class="mission-note">The Tampa Bay chapter of ISC2 is a registered 501(c)(3) educational non-profit. All donations are tax deductible under section 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
